name: Kitty Kombat Multiplayer
description:
JokeCat were running around the streets of Calico city committing crimes everywhere you went.  One day,  BatCat emerged from the darkness, even though it was daytime.

"It's over for you JokeCat!"

"But BatCat! It isn't over until the fat lady sings!"

Neutral Attack: Repeated Kicks

Side Attack: Flying Punch

Up Attack: Jumping Uppercut
